{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0da4d43955","title":"大字报诗——新“贾府”","origin":"《四川省右派言论选辑4》(内部文件，只供领导同志参考，请勿外传和翻印)，中共四川省委宣传部办公室编，1957年7月28日。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1605d5f862","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"0da4d43955"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"0d9be2809a","name":"齐全福"},{"id":"1cc9b81cbb","name":"黄德祖"},{"id":"b4a2bd6afd","name":"李翼之"},{"id":"c0a5e054ec","name":"四川省贸易公司"},{"id":"f51fba5745","name":"胡法刚"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"56267c45cb","type":"title","text":"大字报诗——新“贾府”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0da4d43955"},{"id":"141b51573e","type":"authors","text":"四川省贸易公司齐全福胡法刚李翼之黄德祖","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0da4d43955"},{"id":"8cd86c0d65","type":"subtitle","text":"（省贸易公司干部齐全福、胡法刚、李翼之、黄德祖、罗崇富等）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0da4d43955"},{"id":"eb1cd4b9d8","type":"paragraph","text":"川西公司山西帮，后台老板王厅长，他的部下是穆林，还有助手高步仁。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0da4d43955"},{"id":"56b72b75ae","type":"paragraph","text":"喜新厌旧姚锡均，太上老君郭玉林，笑面老虎韩建中，称王称霸是谢云。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0da4d43955"},{"id":"d3049df22c","type":"paragraph","text":"阿谀奉迎帅文淑，面善心凶黄岫云。姨太作风黄耀芬，阴险毒辣谢汝成。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0da4d43955"},{"id":"1397ebc345","type":"paragraph","text":"上谄下骄陈家英，八面玲珑徐学廉，官小架大曾宪锐，草包饭桶马廷模。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0da4d43955"},{"id":"11f459f240","type":"paragraph","text":"肚皮官司梁国珍，明哲保身候松生，盛气凌人程韫书，吹牛拍马杨仲杰。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0da4d43955"},{"id":"abdcdfec26","type":"paragraph","text":"看人说话乔崇德，阎王作风是肖云，顺风转舵杜丕武，作威作福胡文平。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0da4d43955"},{"id":"2cb70b5860","type":"paragraph","text":"压制批评梅复华，吊二郎当张见阳。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0da4d43955"}],"page":{"id":"584de96c2c","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0da4d43955","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}